fields.description: Specifies the additional columns to be added to source data. Type: array of objects(AdditionalColumns) (or Expression with resultType array of objects).
fields.name: AdditionalColumns

fields.description: The additional HTTP headers in the request to the RESTful API. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: AdditionalHeaders

fields.description: The HTTP request body to the RESTful API if requestMethod is POST. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: RequestBody

fields.description: The HTTP method used to call the RESTful API. The default is GET. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: RequestMethod

fields.description: Specifies the timeout for a HTTP client to get HTTP response from HTTP server. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: RequestTimeout
